messages.content: Write a poem about the sea in 3 lines

Endless waves in dance and play,  
Whisper secrets in salty spray,  
Sky and ocean blend, night meets day.

message_buffer.content:
Vast blue whispers endless,  
Silvery tides kiss the shore,  
Dreams afloat, forevermore.
